                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 123.G35/58.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-09-23">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">September</hi> 23, 1912</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Cuban Secretary of State requests that Bell and I reply to written
                    interrogatories to be sent the Legation from the Audiencia. I request that
                    authorization be granted.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gibson</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
